                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for recovering nickel cobalt lithium manganate waste through pyrogenic calcination",
                    "一种火法煅烧回收镍钴锰酸锂废料的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a recovery method of a lithium nickel cobalt manganese oxide waste material, belongs to the field of waste lithium battery recovery, and solves the problems of large reagent dosage and low recovery rate in a traditional method. The method comprises the following steps: mixing and calcining materials and carbon powder; adding concentrated sulfuric acid into the calcined material, uniformly stirring, roasting, cooling and crushing; adding water to dissolve the crushed material, heating, adding the crushed material, heating, carrying out solid-liquid separation while the solution is hot to obtain manganese sulfate crystals, and cooling the solution to obtain mixed crystals of cobalt sulfate and nickel sulfate; and repeating the operation to enrich lithium, adding sodium hydroxide to obtain a nickel-cobalt-manganese hydroxide mixture and a lithium sulfate solution, and adding sodium carbonate into the solution to separate out lithium carbonate. The method greatly reduces the problem that a large amount of tank storage and transfer liquid is occupied by dilute sulfuric acid and use of a reducing agent hydrogen peroxide in a wet process. Various sulfates are separated out through solubility saturated crystals, and the process is simple and easy to operate. According to the method, the recovery rate of valuable metal lithium is high."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种镍钴锰酸锂废料的回收方法，属于废旧锂电池回收领域，解决了传统方法存在的试剂用量大、回收率低的问题。本发明方法：物料与炭粉混合煅烧；煅烧物料加入浓硫酸搅匀，焙烧冷却后粉碎；粉碎物料加水溶解，升温后再加入粉碎物料，再升温趁热固液分离得到硫酸锰晶体，溶液降温得到硫酸钴和硫酸镍混合晶体；重复操作使锂富集后，加入氢氧化钠得到镍钴锰氢氧化物的混合物以及硫酸锂溶液，该溶液加入碳酸钠析出得到碳酸锂。本发明大大地减少了湿法工艺中稀释硫酸以及使用还原剂双氧水占用大量槽罐储存和中转液体的问题。本发明利用溶解度饱和结晶析出各种硫酸盐，工艺简单易于操作。本发明方法有价金属锂的回收率高。"
                }
            ]
